name: October Goal Achieved
description:
I had a goal to collect NFTs from 1200 different HEN artist and then to collect a total of 5,000 unique NFts in total by the end of October, 2021.  Well today is October 29th and I have reached that goal.  I was not sure I could do it as the month of October has been very hard, sales wise.

To celebrate I am minting this NFT for your collection.
